headline: Dow Launches DOWSIL™ EG-4175 Silicone Gel to Enable Higher Voltage Power Electronics in Electric Vehicles and Renewable Energy Technologies
summary: MIDLAND, Mich., September 04, 2025--New DOWSIL™ EG-4175 Silicone Gel is designed for next-generation insulated gate bipolar transistor (IGBT) modules operating at higher voltages.
